OL,7,FA former PhD student has been found
OL,8,Fguilty of conspiring to commit female
OL,9,Fgenital mutilation against a young
OL,10,Fgirl in the first conviction if its
OL,11,Fkind in England and Wales.
OL,13,FEmad Kaky, who lives in Swansea,
OL,14,Farranged for a child to travel from
OL,15,Fthe UK to Iraq where he had organised
OL,16,Ffor her to be subjected to female
OL,17,Fgenital mutilation (FGM) and forced
OL,18,Finto marriage.
