OL,7,FBut before the crimes could be carried
OL,8,Fout, Kaky's plans were uncovered by a
OL,9,Fwitness who arranged for the victim to
OL,10,Fsafely travel back to the UK.
OL,12,FKaky was arrested and charged with
OL,13,Fconspiracy to commit FGM and forced
OL,14,Fmarriage an offence which he denied.
OL,16,FThe jury were presented evidence that
OL,17,Fhe had booked and paid for a trip to
OL,18,FIraq while living in Nottingham.
